{
  "text": "We begin by recalling the characterization of Z • H (C, M ) and B • H (C, M ) from [CITATION_1] . A DGH-module coalgebra (Θ,D) is a graded H-module coalgebra Θ = ⊕ n≥0 Θ n equipped with an H-linear codifferentialD of degree",
